"2  poblano chiles","2 tablespoons plus 1 teaspoon olive oil, divided","1  large yellow onion, chopped","4  garlic cloves, minced","1 tablespoon chili powder","2 teaspoons sea salt, plus more to taste","2 teaspoons ground cumin","1/2  to 1 teaspoon dried marjoram or dried oregano","1 teaspoon dried fennel","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground pepper, plus more to taste","1  (10-ounce) bottle apple juice, preferably unfiltered","2  (14-ounce) cans chicken broth","1  (14 1/2-ounce) can diced tomatoes","2  bay leaves","2  (15-ounce) cans cannellini beans, garbanzo beans, navy beans, great Northern beans, or hominy (or combination), rinsed and drained","4 cups shredded cooked chicken","1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro leaves","  Garnishes: avocado slices, lime wedges"